Titolo: Maximo vs. Army of Zin

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Maximo vs. Army of Zin (Japanese: 魔界英雄記 マキシモ ～マシンモンスターの野望, Hepburn: Makai Eiyūki Makishimo: Mashin Monsutā no Yabō, lit. Records of the Demon World Hero Maximo: Ambition of the Machine Monsters) is an action-adventure game developed and published by Capcom and developed by their US-based Production Studio 8 in 2003 for the PlayStation 2 video game console. This title is a sequel to Maximo: Ghosts to Glory. It is part of the Ghosts 'n Goblins franchise. It was re-released on the PlayStation Network for the PlayStation 3 in Europe on February 15, 2012.